# 🌍 Travel Tracker CLI App

Welcome to the **Travel Tracker** – a Command Line Interface (CLI) application that helps you track and manage your travel experiences! This project allows users to log their trips, see upcoming and completed journeys, analyze travel statistics, and manage user profiles — all from the terminal.

---

## 🚀 Features

- **User Login System:** Log in using your name and email. New users are created automatically.
- **Add Trips:** Add a new trip by specifying the destination, country, continent, and travel dates.
- **View Trips:**
  - Upcoming trips (future travel plans)
  - Completed trips (past travels)
- **Delete Trips:** Remove any trip by its unique ID.
- **Travel Stats:** View the number of countries and continents you've visited.
- **Profile Info:** Check your registered name, email, and account creation date.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- **Python**
- **SQLAlchemy** (ORM)
- **SQLite** (default local database)
- **Alembic** (for database migrations)



