## 🧪 How to Run

1. **Clone the Repository:**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/travel-tracker-cli.git
cd travel-tracker-cli


Set Up Environment:

Ensure you have Python installed. Then install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run the app
python main.py


